==Outside the ring==
On September 6, 2009, Viloria, who was in attendance at the [[World Cup of Pool]], was chosen to perform the ceremonial break shot before the start of the final match. Because he never played pocket billiards before, Viloria miscued on his first attempt but finally achieved the shot on his second.<ref>{{cite web
