'''Kamel Marek''' (born February 6, 1980 in [[Tizi Ouzou]]) is an [[Algeria]]n [[Association football|footballer]]. He currently plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[USM Alger]] in the [[Algerian Championnat National|Algerian League]].
